<script setup>
import { useNotesStore } from '@/store/index'
import { ref } from 'vue'

const notesStore = useNotesStore()
const note = ref({})
const id = this.$route.params.id

notesStore.notes.forEach(item => {
  item.id === id ? note = item : ''
})

</script>

<template>
  {{ note.title }}
</template>

<style scoped>

</style>
